# MediaHandler.Web — optional local overrides
# Values are loaded from .NET User Secrets automatically (see scripts/generate-env.mjs).
# Use this file only to override specific values without touching the shared secrets store.
# .env is gitignored and never committed.
#
# .NET User Secrets ID: 74395325-16b4-4b59-8a0c-78c9b9afddc1
# Managed via: dotnet user-secrets set "Okta:Domain" "..." --project ..\MediaHandler.API\MediaHandler.API

# Override API base URL (default: https://localhost:7001/api/v1)
# API_BASE_URL=https://localhost:7001/api/v1

# Override Okta credentials (default: read from .NET User Secrets)
# OKTA_ISSUER=https://dev-xxxxx.eu.auth0.com
# OKTA_CLIENT_ID=xxxxx

# Override redirect URI (default: http://localhost:4200/auth/callback)
# OKTA_REDIRECT_URI=http://localhost:4200/auth/callback
